main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Bothell, Washington on January 13, 1961, lasting for 6 minutes.
interesting points: The object was observed for a duration of 6 minutes,The sighting was classified as a Ground-Visual observation,The object was reported to be moving straight and level, The witness had previous sightings in both Bothell and Everett,Washington, A photograph or film was taken during the observation.
witness description: The witness mentioned having had prior sightings of similar objects.
